</span><span class='line'>ERROR<span class="o">:</span> configuration failed <span class="kr">for</span> package ‘rJava’
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">*</span> removing ‘<span class="o">/</span>usr<span class="o">/</span>local<span class="o">/</span>lib<span class="o">/</span>R<span class="o">/</span><span class="m">3.2</span><span class="o">/</span>site<span class="o">-</span>library<span class="o">/</span>rJava’
